0x3F5A61A7.name: GET_WAVE_QUAD_AT_COORDS
0x3F5A61A7.description: This native returns the index of a wave quad if the given point is inside its bounds.

examples.code:
local currentPedPosition = GetEntityCoords(PlayerPedId())
local waveQuadIndex = GetWaveQuadAtCoords(currentPedPosition.x, currentPedPosition.y)

0x3F5A61A7.resultsDescription: The wave quad index at the given position. Returns -1 if there isn't any there.
